7-07-30T22:35:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>首Piano Sonata一開始聽心諗JM9，聽左陣先覺裡面係包羅萬像，雖然香港普遍推Chopin多過Liszt，的確Chopin Average來講係寫得好D，但依首Sonata比大多數Chopin都要有更深層次嘅意思。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聽左一開始頂唔順無聽落去<br />\n<br />\n個人好鐘意佢首Hungarian rhapsody no2 鬼火 mazeppa<br />\n<br />\n反而蕭邦我覺得麻麻<br />\n佢作品比我感覺好 「拿」型 發姣<br />\n我覺得係Too romantic <br />\nMelody 係好聽 但唔係我喜歡的類型<br />\n唔知係咪因爲太多裝飾音"},{"pid":"907f42ba00cdb56454c47d0c587021c1bca8e766","tid":333444,"uid":95571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T22:36:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似好後生就死撚左</blockquote><br />\n <br />\nLiszt 好似七八十歲命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f49b57a4aaf54c7ce8a19de52f6bb6103aa5765c","tid":333444,"uid":95571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T22:39:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鐘意聽rachmaninov多d</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n拉2拉3<br />\n拉3 mvt 2 中間有段我直頭覺得係我聽過所有音樂當中最靚"},{"pid":"2ece90dde724c533d5b981bd6047fe7c5d54660e","tid":333444,"uid":50745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T22:50:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問大家點睇呢位鋼琴家的音樂<br />\n幾鐘意佢有些作品<br />\n<br />\n 鐘<br />\nMazeppa <br />\nLove dream</blockquote><br />\n愛之夢係叫Liebestraum 呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b085bf37daa3b2d268dc13b661ea5e01f67ed28","tid":333444,"uid":50745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T22:51:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好似好後生就死撚左</blockquote><br />\n <br />\nLiszt 好似七八十歲命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n75,6<br />\n1811 1886"},{"pid":"1b7475f3ec93f1a8a7404a01ef6b09a433719abd","tid":333444,"uid":95571,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T23:02:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鐘意聽rachmaninov多d</blockquote><br />\n同埋我覺得古典黎講<br />\n拉赫同莫札特係完全相反 兩個都係極端<br />\n莫札特在於你唔可以用太多感情去彈出感情<br />\n因為莫札特大多數作品都係 非常輕快<br />\n用幾個簡單既音已經砌到哼得出既旋律<br />\nEg ：Turkish march symphony 40 <br />\n         魔笛 don giovanni marriage of figaro       overture <br />\n總之作既音樂係十分清 無雜質<br />\n<br />\n拉赫情感係非常濃郁<br />\n拉3簡直係驚天 相信唔洗多講<br />\n但反而拉赫係用好多個音砌成旋律<br />\n所以兩者每個音都好重要<br />\n兩者都已經係旋律頂尖 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拉2一開始果段真係完全感受到拉赫抑鬱症時既絕望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拉3 ossia cadenza <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n貝多芬都係差少少先去到兩者地位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d00389b413e1b5ddf760821db3f2789c4075a4a2","tid":333444,"uid":95571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T23:06:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鐘意聽rachmaninov多d</blockquote><br />\n同埋我覺得古典黎講<br />\n拉赫同莫札特係完全相反 兩個都係極端<br />\n莫札特在於你唔可以用太多感情去彈出感情<br />\n因為莫札特大多數作品都係 非常輕快<br />\n用幾個簡單既音已經砌到哼得出既旋律<br />\nEg ：Turkish march symphony 40 <br />\n         魔笛 don giovanni marriage of figaro       overture <br />\n總之作既音樂係十分清 無雜質<br />\n<br />\n拉赫情感係非常濃郁<br />\n拉3簡直係驚天 相信唔洗多講<br />\n但反而拉赫係用好多個音砌成旋律<br />\n所以兩者每個音都好重要<br />\n兩者都已經係旋律頂尖 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拉2一開始果段真係完全感受到拉赫抑鬱症時既絕望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拉3 ossia cadenza <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n貝多芬都係差少少先去到兩者地位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n莫札特真係擺好多心機係歌劇 強烈建議一聽<br />\nAbduction from seraglio 一聽就好強土耳其feel"},{"pid":"dd8ac3bf9f83dd6b474dd45b612f3576b2153783","tid":333444,"uid":95571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T23:09:56.000Z","msg":"Bach應該都係神之一<br />\n直接影響 mozart beethoven"},{"pid":"3c185957334ba7653d3f98608639a00c249e22cd","tid":333444,"uid":50745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T23:51:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Bach應該都係神之一<br />\n直接影響 mozart beethoven</blockquote><br />\n音樂之父嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eccd0b206dbac5ad3e4a4f826ed682392a6b266","tid":333444,"uid":124087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T00:35:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好似好後生就死撚左</blockquote><br />\n <br />\nLiszt 好似七八十歲命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n75,6<br />\n1811 1886</blockquote><br />\n搞撚錯左，疏鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b7ed08740ef7ef53c4ba6aa42c9a2c742143846","tid":333444,"uid":117697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T07:04:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>首Piano Sonata一開始聽心諗JM9，聽左陣先覺裡面係包羅萬像，雖然香港普遍推Chopin多過Liszt，的確Chopin Average來講係寫得好D，但依首Sonata比大多數Chopin都要有更深層次嘅意思。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聽左一開始頂唔順無聽落去<br />\n<br />\n個人好鐘意佢首Hungarian rhapsody no2 鬼火 mazeppa<br />\n<br />\n反而蕭邦我覺得麻麻<br />\n佢作品比我感覺好 「拿」型 發姣<br />\n我覺得係Too romantic <br />\nMelody 係好聽 但唔係我喜歡的類型<br />\n唔知係咪因爲太多裝飾音</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n首Sonata感覺係俾Faust影響左 想表達果種善惡對立嘅情戈。所以開始果堆係有意令人不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但1st movement中段開始好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nSecond movement 嘅melody J出血 不過要聽完不安嘅1st嘅不安之後再聽 會有一種解脫嘅feel"},{"pid":"0bb30f959d0666b3a6a19716ae43180e3023fc73","tid":333444,"uid":128062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:20:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鐘意聽rachmaninov多d</blockquote><br />\n同埋我覺得古典黎講<br />\n拉赫同莫札特係完全相反 兩個都係極端<br />\n莫札特在於你唔可以用太多感情去彈出感情<br />\n因為莫札特大多數作品都係 非常輕快<br />\n用幾個簡單既音已經砌到哼得出既旋律<br />\nEg ：Turkish march symphony 40 <br />\n         魔笛 don giovanni marriage of figaro       overture <br />\n總之作既音樂係十分清 無雜質<br />\n<br />\n拉赫情感係非常濃郁<br />\n拉3簡直係驚天 相信唔洗多講<br />\n但反而拉赫係用好多個音砌成旋律<br />\n所以兩者每個音都好重要<br />\n兩者都已經係旋律頂尖 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拉2一開始果段真係完全感受到拉赫抑鬱症時既絕望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拉3 ossia cadenza <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n貝多芬都係差少少先去到兩者地位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nmozart黎講晚期d既piano sonata係正既<br />\n同piano concerto好似20同24<br />\n歌劇好少聽<br />\n比起mozart我又鍾意mendelssohn多d<br />\n<br />\nbeethoven聽開pathetique, tempest, 百聽不厭<br />\n<br />\n推rach既rhapsody on a theme of paganini同prelude op23 no5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"972fc699727585025d397be6550ee8906dce4de0","tid":333444,"uid":128062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:26:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鐘意聽rachmaninov多d</blockquote><br />\n同埋我覺得古典黎講<br />\n拉赫同莫札特係完全相反 兩個都係極端<br />\n莫札特在於你唔可以用太多感情去彈出感情<br />\n因為莫札特大多數作品都係 非常輕快<br />\n用幾個簡單既音已經砌到哼得出既旋律<br />\nEg ：Turkish march symphony 40 <br />\n         魔笛 don giovanni marriage of figaro       overture <br />\n總之作既音樂係十分清 無雜質<br />\n<br />\n拉赫情感係非常濃郁<br />\n拉3簡直係驚天 相信唔洗多講<br />\n但反而拉赫係用好多個音砌成旋律<br />\n所以兩者每個音都好重要<br />\n兩者都已經係旋律頂尖 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拉2一開始果段真係完全感受到拉赫抑鬱症時既絕望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拉3 ossia cadenza <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n貝多芬都係差少少先去到兩者地位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n莫札特真係擺好多心機係歌劇 強烈建議一聽<br />\nAbduction from seraglio 一聽就好強土耳其feel</blockquote><br />\n推薦 schubert d940同dvorak piano quintet no2 op81"},{"pid":"808ef2a0aa8ea74e9513c2f686cef5723675e100","tid":333444,"uid":128062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:28:00.000Z","msg":"btw 你提到turkish march...真係一定要聽glenn gould版"}]}